{"tid":2182592,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解連登個世界可以同現實嘅香港差咁遠","createTime":"2020-08-31T11:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:36:17.000Z","uid":56498,"like":76,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"921df0b5c0110d2bb24b1be909b5d6089a7aa1a9","tid":2182592,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"講下自己d個人經驗<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟仲係大學生果陣，參加左舊登唔知邊鳩個社工搞嘅免費食麥當勞聚會，諗住識下差唔多年紀嘅巴絲打啦<br />\n<br />\n個聚會一開波坐底就叫人自我介紹，咁我就介紹自己係好普通的city仔，中意咩興趣咁<br />\n<br />\n點知身邊d人一聽到係讀緊city，嘩屌個個都好似用勁adore的眼神望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「嘩我都好想升city」<br />\n「我讀緊ive炸屌」<br />\n<br />\n明明起舊登，非三大基本上只係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但起D濕鳩聚會都畀人當神咁拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住起連登上班台又係，個個都話正常畢業無耐應該搵3萬4萬<br />\n<br />\n入啲谷吹水，我屌勁撚多人打份19工然後討論點考ACO 低級紀律部隊或者安全佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果D輕鬆搵幾皮嘅唔知去晒邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaad6e69f6a8a5aede4bf8db85d5ecd29db0c20","tid":2182592,"uid":81273,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"廢人唔會出聲<br />\n勁人衝出黎威 <br />\n有幾奇 你ig都報喜不報憂"},{"pid":"bdf14b2b3cfbb61bb629a33f9568b69c859b3456","tid":2182592,"uid":264067,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"樓主第一日上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd5ba464beaf354203a0489ff1e0443ea9694f2","tid":2182592,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:54:33.